  "texts": [
    "It can be used across various agricultural applications, including field crops, vegetables, fruits, herbs, flowers, and even hydroponic systems.",
    "Its compatibility with different growing systems makes it adaptable to a wide range of market segments, enhancing its appeal to farmers and gardeners alike (Nyakeri et al., 2017; Wang & Shelomi, 2017).",
    "While the use of BSF frass is not yet as widespread as other fertilizers, there is a growing awareness of its benefits and potential.",
    "As more research and information become available, along with increased adoption and success stories from early adopters, market awareness and demand for BSF frass are expected to expand.",
    "Overall, the market potential for BSF frass is promising, driven by the increasing demand for sustainable agriculture, organic products, and effective waste management solutions."
  ]
